  <name>COSMIC Hue</name>
  <summary>Control Philips Hue lights from your COSMIC desktop</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      COSMIC Hue is a system tray applet for the COSMIC desktop environment that provides 
      quick and easy control of your Philips Hue smart lighting system.
    </p>
    <p>
      Features include automatic bridge discovery, control of individual lights and groups, 
      brightness and color adjustment with an integrated color picker, quick access to scenes, 
      and support for multiple languages.
    </p>
  </description>
  
